data.description: Fall in love with this beautiful home in "The Falls" gated community in highly-rated Blue Springs schools! Tons of living space and a gorgeous, landscaped yard! Step in and you'll appreciate the large great room w/ boxed ceiling, fireplace and plenty of daylight streaming in! You'll enjoy cooking in the spacious kitchen w/ lots of cabinets, pull-out drawers, Jenn-air cooktop and plenty of countertop space! Enjoy meals at the table surrounded by windows that bring in the outdoors! The formal dining is great for entertaining. Huge primary bedroom is on main level and has its own deck overlooking yard. The spacious primary bath has jetted tub and his/her walk-in closets! Head upstairs to 3 bedrooms, one w/ private bath and other bedrooms w/ own vanity and shared bath. Tiled bath floors are heated! All bedrooms have walk-in closets! Nice attic space is easy to access with full-size door. Finished walkout basement offers more great living space...family room w/ fireplace, workout room, office space, full bath and stubbed for wet bar. The utility garage offers large workshop area w/ daylight window and features built-ins, sink and storage area plus direct access to bath. Backyard is a dream with all the work done for you! This spring, you'll enjoy the gorgeous landscaping w/ beautiful perennials and a peaceful water feature! There's plenty of room for entertaining w/ all the deck space! Sellers have done a great job caring for this home! More to appreciate...whole house stereo and water softener, reverse osmosis in kitchen, central vac, both fireplaces converted in 2021 to zero emission w/ easy on/off and provide heat. New roof and gutters w/ leaf-guard in 2023, both HVAC units new in 2021, new Andersen windows in bsmt and over primary tub in 2020, baths updates w/ granite/quartz counters, vessel sinks and tile work in 2017. The Falls is a quaint, gated community located close to I-70 & 470 Hwys and offers a variety of shopping and dining plus medical facilities close by!
